rComments: Very nice and helpful teacher. Goes out of her way to make sure all of the students are on track.
She is really helpful if you have questions or concerns, and if you put in the work, you will gets lots of useful feedback. She's nice, too, and easy to talk to.

I was pleasantly surprised at how passionate she was about her student's success. I remember her meeting with me a couple times outside of class to help me perfect my papers and really taking the time to explain certain concepts to me. Taking this class will not only improve your writing, but you will want to take more english classes after!
Very concerned teacher. I learned a lot.
